S . Africa maize futures turnover hits record in May . South Africa ' s maize futures market , launched last year , notched up record turnover worth 106 million rand in May , the South African Futures Exchange ( Safex ) said . Turnover since the beginning of 1997 totalled over 305 million rand , it added . Deliveries of 44 , 900 tonnes of maize were made through Safex on the May contracts . - - Johannesburg newsroom + 27 11 482 1003 
